author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 240
acceptance_criteria: A variadic positional can be declared passthrough (or '--' separator is respected and stripped) so -h/--help/--json tokens after it reach the handler verbatim at the real CLI boundary; global help still renders for the command when no passthrough content is present; behavior covered by real-boundary regression tests including an extension variadic command; contract docs + generated CLI contracts document the opt-out
